00:03:31.020 --> 00:03:36.699
I did expect that my comrades in the Republican movement

00:03:36.699 --> 00:03:39.460
might have come to help us.

00:03:39.460 --> 00:03:43.020
It didn't come at all.

00:03:43.020 --> 00:03:49.210
I was studying the Bible three weeks with one of Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:03:49.210 --> 00:03:52.689
He was very English and his wife saw English.

00:03:52.689 --> 00:03:57.289
I wouldn't have chosen them to have come into my house, but they did.

00:03:57.289 --> 00:03:59.169
